ets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:51:00.000Z","msg":"要申請好似至少三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a9b8af6717af846716ec6940cf0e3c5d07f7ce","tid":546393,"uid":169413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有d地方要搞手續都唔煩<br />\n睇岩左就搵當地既動物機構問點做<br />\n成個過程會易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我其實係唔係好識程序上嘅嘢<br />\n仲要唔知當地有咩機構可以搵到<br />\n同埋聽講空運嘅話個過程會嚇死D動物<br />\n<br />\n不過都冇用, 我已經返咗香港<br />\n臨走之前都見唔到佢<br />\n好有衝動想飛返去搵佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>要申請好似至少三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇海關個網帶動物入香港好似仲要擺係漁農署幾個月 確保冇傳染病先比返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但漁農署啲環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我見到有個fb page叫琉球皇oki（好似係）<br />\n係有個香港人係日本旅行嗰陣執咗隻流浪貓仲帶返埋返香港"},{"pid":"44bf5af0493cdf1bc587383f1dee47346402915b","tid":546393,"uid":47819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5dc9fa91e63eee6d0e139997a8df971b0095840e","tid":546393,"uid":31182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"55a3f83d47b84d3e59713de3ef49cc601b3258fb","tid":546393,"uid":47819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"其實有d地方要搞手續都唔煩<br />\n睇岩左就搵當地既動物機構問點做<br />\n成個過程會易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"我其實係唔係好識程序上嘅嘢<br />\n仲要唔知當地有咩機構可以搵到<br />\n同埋聽講空運嘅話個過程會嚇死D動物<br />\n<br />\n不過都冇用, 我已經返咗香港<br />\n臨走之前都見唔到佢<br />\n好有衝動想飛返去搵佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"咁唔識咪去學、去問...<br />\n睇下有冇心既啫<br />\n<br />\n空運既話未必會嚇死... <br />\n除非特別細膽、或者健康本身有問題etc<br />\n所以咪要問當地動物機構<br />\n因為通常都順便會睇埋獸醫<br />\n問埋獸醫意見佢適唔適合運走"},{"pid":"8f6659eefce6fedf988463a23b7323d6233232f8","tid":546393,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91fdbb93a0ff78209cfa4eb66b211cdd0d9e2c89","tid":546393,"uid":169413,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T14:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b718f391d72cbe3b969dfc816f083625a9fcc2e","tid":546393,"uid":31182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34a9b8af6717af846716ec6940cf0e3c5d07f7ce","tid":546393,"uid":169413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有d地方要搞手續都唔煩<br />\n睇岩左就搵當地既動物機構問點做<br />\n成個過程會易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我其實係唔係好識程序上嘅嘢<br />\n仲要唔知當地有咩機構可以搵到<br />\n同埋聽講空運嘅話個過程會嚇死D動物<br />\n<br />\n不過都冇用, 我已經返咗香港<br />\n臨走之前都見唔到佢<br />\n好有衝動想飛返去搵佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>要申請好似至少三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇海關個網帶動物入香港好似仲要擺係漁農署幾個月 確保冇傳染病先比返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但漁農署啲環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我見到有個fb page叫琉球皇oki（好似係）<br />\n係有個香港人係日本旅行嗰陣執咗隻流浪貓仲帶返埋返香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"我知係要時間, 如果等幾個月就得嘅話又有咩所謂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afcd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fquarantine%2Fqua_ie%2Fqua_ie_ipab%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc.html&d=R30zzq6Y5Ox1rj7voRlCxGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=2af0af6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/